title: Jimi Hendrix-Uncut 1967-'70 Documentary (the best
description:
Hey All,
    The IMDB discription really doesn\&#039;t tell anything here, but this is Jimi Hendrix-Uncut Part 3-1967-\&#039;70. Probably the best part of this series at least to me, a fan for years. 
    This is a documentary, NOT a musical preformance although you can\&#039;t do such a thing without including segments of certian preformances etc. I found this to be very good and a well done film that includes interviews with many of the people who knew Jimi best. Musicians and friends alike including segments from Jimi himself. Great stuff.
                                                                    srw567
